::DeathScythe::

Growling, DeathScythe walks over to Zyber, limping a bit. He looks 
her over, wondering if he should just kill her. He didn't really have 
anywhere to hurry to...

"Shut up, femm," he says, a fist lashing out at Zyber's face.
